D\":\"81292\",\"Description\":\"LR81292\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1594930101MODTR81292IVO5079_HiRes.jpg?\"}]},\"description\":\"The Modern Traditions collection offers a lovely style no matter what room you place it in. If you\'re searching for a piece that combines traditional style with a well toned palette than look no further! Perfect in the foyer, dining area, or even office space, this intricate piece is ready to thrill you and your guests. The bordered edge also provides a beautiful transition from detailed patterns to carpet or hardwood flooring. Bring a masterpiece home today!\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1594930101MODTR81292IVO5079_HiRes.jpg\"},\"Criss Cross\":{\"title\":\"Criss Cross\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Criss Cross\",\"Description\":\"Criss Cross\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1655537137CRISS81297GRY5079_HiRes Main.jpg?\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"81295\",\"Description\":\"LR81295\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1630045920CRISS81295NVI90C0_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81296\",\"Description\":\"LR81296\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1630046009CRISS81296SIV90C0_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81300\",\"Description\":\"LR81300\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1630046457CRISS81300BRE90C0_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81297\",\"Description\":\"LR81297\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1655537137CRISS81297GRY5079_HiRes Main.jpg?\"}]},\"description\":\"Bringing the Criss Cross collection into your home will make for quite the thrill. The crisp lines to this collection are sure to draw the eye whether you place it within a living area, foyer, dining area, or even office space. The deeper background hue allows for attention without overwhelming the space. The grid design is modern and functional; the perfect mix with a variety of different interior styles. Don\'t overlook this piece\'s ability to transform a space with great style.\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1630046457CRISS81300BRE90C0_HiRes.jpg\"},\"Infinity\":{\"title\":\"Infinity\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Infinity\",\"Description\":\"Infinity\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1595120675INFIN81308BKG5272_HiRes.jpg?\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"81308\",\"Description\":\"LR81308\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1595120675INFIN81308BKG5272_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81309\",\"Description\":\"LR81309\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1594992753INFIN81309WBL7995_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81313\",\"Description\":\"LR81313\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1594992894INFIN81313GYB7995_HiRes.jpg?\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81319\",\"Description\":\"LR81319\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1594993029INFIN81319LSB7995_HiRes.jpg?\"}]},\"description\":\"Bold patterns in dark, rich colors identify the Infinity Collection. This collection\'s color palette accents a wide variety of styles. Also featuring distressed abstract designs allows for years of usage without the appearance of wear. The possibilities are endless with this versatile piece so don\'t be afraid to place it in the foyer, add it to the bedroom, or even in an office space. The low pile height is also a great advantage; ideal size if you have a family member with a trip hazard. Bring this lovely piece home today and enjoy its style for years to come!\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1595120675INFIN81308BKG5272_HiRes.jpg\"},\"Karma\":{\"title\":\"Karma\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Karma\",\"Description\":\"Karma\",\"ImageName\":\"B2BImages\\/Full_Images\\/1594990809KARMA21043NAV90C0_HiRes.jpg?\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"Des