images\\/Product\\/1594929951MODTR81291BEO5079_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81292\",\"Description\":\"LR81292\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594930101MODTR81292IVO5079_HiRes.jpg\"}]},\"description\":\"The Modern Traditions collection offers a lovely style no matter what room you place it in. If you\'re searching for a piece that combines traditional style with a well toned palette than look no further! Perfect in the foyer, dining area, or even office space, this intricate piece is ready to thrill you and your guests. The bordered edge also provides a beautiful transition from detailed patterns to carpet or hardwood flooring. Bring a masterpiece home today!\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1594930101MODTR81292IVO5079_HiRes.jpg\"}}\";', '2022-06-24 22:53:47', '2022-10-07 04:18:40', NULL);
