ttp:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1594319441ACCEN70153TNV2639_Web.jpg\"},\"Classic Jute\":{\"title\":\"Classic Jute\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Classic Jute\",\"Description\":\"Classic Jute\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594327958CLASS81206GYN3656_Web.jpg\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"False\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"False\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"81206\",\"Description\":\"LR81206\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594327958CLASS81206GYN3656_Web.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81207\",\"Description\":\"LR81207\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594327907CLASS81207GRY3656_Web.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81208\",\"Description\":\"LR81208\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594327926CLASS81208GAB3656_Web.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81209\",\"Description\":\"LR81209\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1594327860CLASS81209NAT3656_Web.jpg\"}]},\"description\":\"Jute is the perfect addition for today\'s contemporary home. This collection truly highlights a lovely, natural feel in the home and merges with a variety of different decor and styles. Braided jute construction exhibits naturally anti-static, insulating and moisture regulating properties. Whether it is in a living area, entryway, or even dining area, this collection is sure to please you and your guests.\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1594327958CLASS81206GYN3656_Web.jpg\"},\"Kilimanjaro\":{\"title\":\"Kilimanjaro\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Kilimanjaro\",\"Description\":\"Kilimanjaro\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009057NATUR12032NGY40RD_HiRes.jpg\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"False\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"False\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"12032\",\"Description\":\"LR12032\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009057NATUR12032NGY40RD_HiRes.jpg\"}]},\"description\":\"The Kilimanjaro rug collection transcends traditional geometric motifs of the past and establishes new summits of cutting-edge elegance within indoor and outdoor spaces. This neutral addition features a minimal Greek key bordering to frame your room and bring a sophisticated flair to your atmosphere. This rug features a balanced blend of modern monochromatic shades. From afar, this floor covering appears gray and white; however, the closer you look, the more intricate this inviting assortment of anthracite, gray, white, and cream tones becomes.\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1595009057NATUR12032NGY40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},\"Natural Jute\":{\"title\":\"Natural Jute\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Natural Jute\",\"Description\":\"Natural Jute\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595014974NATUR50135NAT2030.jpg\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"False\",\"Clearence\":\"False\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"False\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"50134\",\"Description\":\"LR50134 - JUTE ROUND BRAID\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009709NATUR50134NAT40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"50135\",\"Description\":\"LR50135 - JUTE OVAL BRAID\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595014974NATUR50135NAT2030.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"50136\",\"Description\":\"LR50136 - JUTE BREADED\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009740NATUR50136NAT40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12029\",\"Description\":\"LR12029\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595008831NATUR12029NAT40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12030\",\"Description\":\"LR12030\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595008975NATUR12030NAT40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12031\",\"Description\":\"LR12031\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009032NATUR12031NAT40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12032\",\"Description\":\"LR12032\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009057NATUR12032NGY40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12033\",\"Description\":\"LR12033\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009082NATUR12033GRY40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12034\",\"Description\":\"LR12034\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009136NATUR12034GRY40RD_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12035\",\"Description\":\"LR12035\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009169NATUR12035NGY57OV_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12036\",\"Description\":\"LR12036\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009242NATUR12036NGY57OV_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12038\",\"Description\":\"LR12038\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009283NATUR12038BHG57OV_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"12039\",\"Description\":\"LR12039\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1595009393NATUR12039BHG40RD_HiRes.jpg\"}]},\"description\":\"Hand braided from the jute of India, the Natural Jute Collection is handcrafted for your home with delicate and unique skill found in every piece. These pieces features a boutique style with a floral flare design, created by intricate braiding and weaving throughout every piece. The natural tone to the jute makes this piece an easy addition to a variety of spaces. Bring it home today for a spectacular new addition to your home!\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1595014974NATUR50135NAT2030.jpg\"},\"Nimroz\":{\"title\":\"Nimroz\",\"raw\":{\"CollectionID\":\"Nimroz\",\"Description\":\"Nimroz\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1642749879NMROZ81983MLT2030_HiRes.jpg\",\"NewArrivalExpiry\":\"True\",\"Clearence\":\"False\",\"TopSeller\":\"False\",\"SpecialBuy\":\"False\",\"DesignsList\":[{\"DesignID\":\"81980\",\"Description\":\"LR81980\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1628681240NMROZ81980BMU7999_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81981\",\"Description\":\"LR81981\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1628681465NMROZ81981BMU7999_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81982\",\"Description\":\"LR81982\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1628681557NMROZ81982BEM7999_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81983\",\"Description\":\"LR81983\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1642749879NMROZ81983MLT2030_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81984\",\"Description\":\"LR81984\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1628681748NMROZ81984NML7999_HiRes.jpg\"},{\"DesignID\":\"81985\",\"Description\":\"LR81985\",\"ImageName\":\"images\\/Product\\/1628681820NMROZ81985BMU7999_HiRes.jpg\"}]},\"description\":\"Combining centuries of traditional textile techniques with contemporary customer needs, this boho-chic diamond dynasty geometric striped area rug is an innovative blend of classic dhurrie construction and a secondary cotton backing for extra support and durability. This flatwoven rug is handmade by artisan weavers using natural jute and cotton fibers for a sustainable, stylish look and feel. The vivid natural colors and rejuvenated mix of geometry motifs showcase time-tested weaving techniques while preserving the traditional craft of dhurrie area rug construction. Trimmed with a natural loom fringe, this finishing border adds a touch of texture to your space.\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/lrhome.us\\/images\\/Product\\/1642749879NMROZ81983MLT2030_HiRes.jpg\"}}\";', '2022-06-24 22:58:32', '2022-06-24 22:59:23', NULL),
