(24, 1, '{\"_token\":\"T8rJDkIyXWC7BtYxmzlde9PvxM5vOCQH7ou5X0Pz\",\"name\":\"Olga\",\"subject\":\"Cooperation offer\",\"email\":\"olga@anatolianweavers.com\",\"phone\":\"00903423570632\",\"company\":\"Anatolian weavers carpets\",\"city\":\"Gaziantep\",\"state\":\"Turkey\",\"message\":\"Greetings,\\r\\nI hope you are doing well. First of all, I want to introduce myself. My name is Olga. I am a sales representative of manufacturer Anatolian weavers carpets. We started our production with yarn in 1996 and became as one of the most important manufacturers in the industry. Now, we produce different types of carpets in Gaziantep, Turkey. We are working with more than 20 different countries such as USA, Great Britain, Germany, UAE, Qatar, Italy, Australia etc. \\r\\nNowadays, we offer our clients high quality carpets with unique design and in different materials.\\r\\nWe would like to offer you cooperation with our manufacture. Please, let me know if you are interested in cooperation and I will share our catalogue with you.\\r\\nFeel free to contact me if you have any questions.\\r\\nLook forward to hearing from you soon.\\r\\nHave a good day\"}', '2022-10-24 19:50:42', '2022-10-24 19:50:42', NULL),
