(34, 1, '{\"_token\":\"FSJz3dWI8TCGd64GQYqof1ov6VDcViaMvJThlTi1\",\"name\":\"Anshul Grover\",\"subject\":\"Meet ANJ Textiles\",\"email\":\"info@anjtextiles.com\",\"phone\":\"9896925000\",\"company\":\"ANJ TEXTILES\",\"city\":\"panipat\",\"state\":\"haryana\",\"message\":\"Hi, \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nI am Anshul from ANJ Textiles (INDIA).\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nAs you are importing textiles products from India. We are manufacturers in Panipat (India) and can give you the best quality and at less price at which you are taking currently\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are proudly accredited with the international manufacturing association - Sedex Compliance Certification.\\r\\n \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nWe manufacture Macrame pouf, Woven pouf, Cotton Woven Pouf , Jute woven pouf, wall hangings, table runner, placements, Kitchen linen and terry towels, rugs\\/ chindi rugs, mats, Rope baskets, jute bags, bed sheets, throws, blankets, bath mats, Chair pad,  canvas\\/cotton bags, Kitchen Linen, towels, macrame items, duries,  cotton\\/macrame baskets, carpet, Mexican falsa blanket,  wool blankets, Poncho, cushion covers, Acrylic plus polyester blankets, poufs, pillow, duvets, etc in Panipat, India, Since 1991.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nWe have specialization in all kinds of Macrame range, Wool rugs, macrame bags, rugs,Jute Braided Rugs, throws, Pouffe, Chair-pads, cushions and bathmats.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe can give you the same products at better prices and quality. \\r\\nPlease give us chance to serve you.\\u200b\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nPlease reply to ask for Best Quotes and Samples. We would be glad to serve you. \\r\\n\\r\\nRegards\\r\\n\\r\\nAnshul Grover\\r\\n\\r\\nMarketing Director \\r\\n\\r\\nwww.Anjtextiles.com\\r\\n\\r\\ninfo@anjtextiles.com\\r\\n\\r\\nCall - +919896925000\"}', '2022-10-29 15:15:02', '2022-10-29 15:15:02', NULL),
