(36, 1, '{\"_token\":\"KhGRWGUTuF91YHY2WNBxIecn9SJxIiNZ4n9wFfdN\",\"name\":\"RASHID MALIK\",\"subject\":\"BUSINEES PROPOSAL\",\"email\":\"rashid@mapleartsindia.com\",\"phone\":\"00919837214803\",\"company\":\"Maple Arts India\",\"city\":\"Saharanpur\",\"state\":\"Utter Pradesh\",\"message\":\"Dear Sir\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are manufacturer and supplier of Indian handicrafts items. Such as we manufacture wooden & Iron handicrafts items. Furniture, decorative items, wooden table top items, Dining table And chair, wall hangings, candle holder, kitchen accessories, Ceramic drawer boxes, wooden carved decorative penal and all other items which can be prepared in wood.\\r\\n                       \\r\\nWe always use seasoned and pre-treated wood and hence they have a long life. If you inform us about your area of interest we will be very much pleased to send you more photos our regular items.\\r\\nFor your kind information we are fully capable to translate any idea into reality and in this way we developed many new items which were proved very popular in the international market.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe want to long lasting business relation with you and assure you of our best co-operation.\\r\\n,\\r\\nThanks With Best Regards\\r\\nRashid Malik\\r\\nMaple Arts India\\r\\n11B\\/3624 Ali ki chungi\\r\\n Saharanpur 247001 UP India\\r\\nContect No. +91 7017880047 \\r\\nWhatsApp No. +91 9837214803\\r\\nEmail:-  mapleartsindia@gmail.com \\/ rashid@mapleartsindia.com\\r\\nweb  :- www.mapleartsindia.com\"}', '2022-10-30 13:56:26', '2022-10-30 13:56:26', NULL),
