(61, 1, '{\"_token\":\"A3A3qGohFQzMBOT9OozorRveyBGBCB2ZpGNS6aqA\",\"name\":\"Vishnuraj\",\"subject\":\"Jute rugs\",\"email\":\"unicoir@gmail.com\",\"phone\":\"919895299052\",\"company\":\"United COir Factrories\",\"city\":\"Alleppey\",\"state\":\"Kerala\",\"message\":\"Dear Sir, \\r\\n \\r\\nHanmade chunky Jute Rugs\\r\\n \\r\\n            We introduce ourselves as one of the leading Manufactures and Exporters of Coir,Jute Rugs from India . All rugs are available with latex backed (for non-slipping) and without latex. We are in the business since 1935 and we manufacture most modern designs in Rugs of Excellent Quality at most competitive prices than any other suppliers from India. \\r\\n \\r\\nHANDSPUN JUTE RUGS \\r\\nSIZE:- 24\\u201dX36\\u201d :-US$ 3.85 PER PCE FOB COCHIN\\r\\nSIZE: 3\\u2019X5\\u2019 :- US$ 9.61 PER PCE FOB COCHIN\\r\\nSIZE: 4\\u2019X6\\u2019:- US$ 15.38 PER PCE FOB COCHIN\\r\\nSIZE :- 5\\u2019X8\\u2019 :- US$ 25.63  PER PCE FOB COCHIN\\r\\nLOADABILITY :- 4100 SQMTER IN 1X40HC\\r\\n \\r\\n \\r\\n \\r\\n        We provide timely shipment and easy terms of payment. We have lot of unique designs and our company has been serving customers in  US & European countries for more than 15 years without any customer complaints on quality.\\r\\n.\\r\\nPlease do let us know your interest in adding us to your vendors list for serving your firm with our hand -skill quality of our workers.We do our 95% business to USA and we are sure of serving your requirements to the best class service and pricing targets to meet your clients retail targets.\\r\\n \\r\\nThanking you in advance,\\r\\n \\r\\nBest Regards\\r\\n \\r\\n \\r\\nVISHNURAJ.B\\r\\nEXPORT EXECUTIVE\\r\\nTHE UNITED COIR FACTORIES\\r\\n(AN ISO90001-2008 CERTIFIED COMPANY)\\r\\nKERALA,INDIA.\\r\\nPHONE :- +91 477 2243832\\r\\nFAX:- +91 477 2243119\\r\\nE-MAIL :- unicoir@gmail.com\"}', '2022-11-08 17:43:46', '2022-11-08 17:43:46', NULL),
