(101, 1, '{\"_token\":\"VHqCX8kyPwQqv1ueFHXWbGX7NQi5420d0qGRVGES\",\"name\":\"Ashok\",\"subject\":\"Supply of Home Textiles\",\"email\":\"ashok@luxtexkrr.com\",\"phone\":\"00919840625431\",\"company\":\"LAKSTEX\",\"city\":\"Karur\",\"state\":\"Tamilnadu, India\",\"message\":\"Hi,\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are one of the manufacturer and exporters of Home Textiles.\\r\\nBelow is our company brief profile and go through to know about us:\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u2022\\tCompany Name: Laks Tex\\r\\n\\u2022\\tEstablished: 2008\\r\\n\\u2022\\tManaging Director: Murugesan K\\r\\n\\u2022\\t8\\/121, AMARAVATHI NAGAR, ANDANKOVIL EAST, KARUR-639002, TAMIL NADU, INDIA\\r\\n\\u2022\\tLast year turnover \\u2013 US$5.00 Million\\r\\n\\u2022\\tHaving own weaving, Embroidery, socks, length hemming, automatic glove dye cut and 200 sewing machines\\r\\n\\u2022\\tAlso having own poly and cotton filling units\\r\\n\\u2022\\tOur Products: Apron, Glove, Potholder, Double glove, kitchen towel, dishcloth, bread basket, Table cloth, placemat, runner, napkin, Cushions, curtain, box cushion, chair pad , hammock, lounge mat, cotton bags and shower curtain.\\r\\n\\u2022\\tCertifications: WALMART, ISO 9001, SA 8000, OEKO-TEX APPENDIX 6,GRS, OCS and GOTS \\r\\n\\u2022\\tOur customers; \\r\\nUSA \\u2013 PBS Home goods, VCNY, Cotton valley, Marco polo, Lintex linens, Unique sourcing, Home Essentials  & Tribal design.\\r\\nFrance \\u2013 Bouchara, Becquet, and CP International\\r\\nSweden \\u2013 Camacamina and East Import\\r\\nCanada \\u2013 Bouclair\\r\\nAustralia \\u2013 lIncraft, Mittal and Perago.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are looking forward your valuable reply with your enquiries to quote or develop.\\r\\n\\r\\nWith regards.\\r\\n\\r\\nAshok\"}', '2022-12-12 19:25:51', '2022-12-12 19:25:51', NULL),
