(1175, 16, 'document_url_5', NULL, '2022-05-10 19:49:04', '2022-05-10 19:49:04', NULL),
(1216, 15, 'about_us_description_1', '<p>Dear Partners,</p>\r\n             \r\n              <p>LR Home is a family-owned-and-operated business devoted to stylish home\r\n                décor and design. Founded in 2001 with a vision to be a customer-first supplier,\r\n                we are passionate about creating innovative and essential products for every\r\n                home. Our passions are showcased by blending unique designs and textures at\r\n                price points that appeal to all tastes and styles. </p>\r\n             \r\n              <p>By purchasing an LR Home product, you directly support our education and\r\n                healthcare initiatives in Dalton, GA, and Mirzapur, India. From our hands to your\r\n                home, the home décor made from LR comes from a place of love and passion\r\n                for customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n             \r\n              <p>Over the years, LR Home has evolved from being an area rug distributor into a\r\n                multi-faceted home interior supplier. Our 2021 catalog showcases our evolution\r\n                with a home décor line consisting of over 1,000 products. In June, we will take\r\n                another exciting step in our journey by launching our furniture line.</p>\r\n            \r\n              <p>LR Home firmly believes in delivering value and style with Quality, Honesty,\r\n                Humility, Trust and Transparency to hit a price point. That is why we offer a wide\r\n                variety of designed collections with prices that fit almost all budgets. We look\r\n                forward to growing our partnerships and providing the quality, innovation, and\r\n                value that are the trademarks of the LR Home brand. </p>\r\n             \r\n              <p>Sincerely,<br>\r\n                Rajani Laddha | Shri Krishna Laddha</p>', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
(1217, 15, 'about_us_image_1', 'https://lrhome.us/media/images/rug-makker2.jpg', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
(1218, 15, 'about_us_description_2', '<p>The origins of carpet making and intricate weaves have their roots in a small yet dynamic city in India called Mirzapur. Krishna Laddha and Rajani Laddha belong to this town which is renowned all over the world for creating the most exotic weaves that one has ever seen! They have founded a legacy of creativity and community through hand-crafted home décor. In pursuit of their dream, the Laddhas’ emigrated to Dalton, GA, and decided to build an institution focused on people, partnerships, and philanthropy. In 2001, they laid the foundation of this dream with LR Home- a wholesale area rug business. Krishna and Rajani capitalized on their expertise in textiles, expanding to bring unique designs and textures to the home décor and furniture industry. </p>\r\n                <p>At LR Home, we have a deep and abiding commitment to positively impact society while delivering premium products. Our organization founded the Laddha Academy in Mirzapur to help underprivileged children by supplementing their education with after-school tutoring, leadership training, and scholarships. This program is just one of the many initiatives contributing to our goals of giving back to our communities. </p>', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
(1219, 15, 'about_us_image_2', 'https://lrhome.us/media/images/rug-makker3.jpg', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
(1220, 15, 'about_us_description_3', '<p>LR Home has now grown to be an organization of more than ﬁfty associates from across the globe. The members of our team are a family and act according to the  principles of honesty, integrity and respect laid out by the founders. At the helm of this operation are their sons - Vaibhav and Vinamra. They look forward to a future of expansions while maintaining their \r\n                  parents’ original goal: grow together and give back to the community.</p>', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
(1221, 15, 'about_us_image_3', 'https://lrhome.us/media/images/rug-makker4.jpg', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', '2022-05-26 16:52:27', NULL),
